bodyText: Would you like to show off with your beer pong skills? How about winning a trip abroad to play beer pong?

Your dreams are coming true! In the autumn 2017 the biggest beer pong clubs in Finland, Aalto Beer Pong and Beer Pong Turku, will co-operate and arrange a Finnish Series of Beer Pong tournament. The main prize of the tournament will be a trip with accommodation to the next European Series of Beer Pong held in the beginning of 2018.
More information about the tournament and ticket sales coming during the spring, stay tuned!
